---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Roles & permissions">
  <h1>Roles & permissions</h1>

  <p>Three roles: Member, Editor, Administrator. Cumulative — Editor includes Member rights, Administrator includes Editor rights.</p>
  <h2>Member</h2>
  <p>Public site + member-only content + own profile + group membership + prayer requests + connect card.</p>
  <h2>Editor</h2>
  <p>Adds the admin shell. Can create + edit Pages, News, Blog, Sermons, Events, Classes, Documents, Leaders, Service Times, Connect Card moderation, Prayer Request moderation, Volunteer roles + signups view, Broadcasts.</p>
  <h2>Administrator</h2>
  <p>Adds Site Settings (all tabs) + User Management (create / edit / lock / hard delete users) + Email Templates + Audit Log full read.</p>
</BaseLayout>
